-- U.K. Stocks Little Changed Before Bernanke Testimony
-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 2013-07-18T07:12:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-18/u-k-stocks-little-changed-before-bernanke-testimony.html
U.K. stocks were little changed as
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S. Bernanke  prepared for a second
day of testimony to Congress.  The FTSE 100 Index slipped 2.27 points, or less than 0.1
percent, to 6,569.66 at 8:11 a.m. in London, having earlier lost
as much as 0.3 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  